        <h4>"Talk about your feelings!"<br><span>It's ok to breakdown to a loved one and tell them what you're going through or how you're feeling. Helplines are also great. Once you start talking, your burdens are lifted! It really feels nice.</span></h4>
      </div>
      <div class="item">
        <h4>"Take a break!"<br><span>It's not always about work! Take regular breaks and do something relaxing. Yoga is a great way to chill and relax your mind. There are many tutorials on Youtube for the best yoga routine!</span></h4>
      </div>
      <div class="item">
        <h4>"Do something you're good at!"<br><span>Often we think we're not good at anything. Well, this is the perfect opportunity for self-discovery. Do something that makes you happy! This is a great way to accept who you are!</span></h4>
      </div>
